('38218','deDE','Preserving The Lore','Collect $1oa Stones of Remembrance.','<A cool breeze of thought and memory enters your mind as you touch the strangely glowing stone. Within an instant, the purpose of this stone has been made manifest.>\n\n<You realize that what you hold is a Stone of Remembrance, an object imbued with druidic knowledge and lore. The greedy Stoneblood harpies must have stolen these precious artifacts from the druids in Thas\'talah. You decide to search for more of these missing stones and return them to the Archdruid of Lore.>','','','','','','Return to E\'lothir at Thas\'talah.','21287'),
