('38219','deDE','Defending The Grove','Slay $1oa Harpies involved in the attack on Thas\'talah.','The harpies have had a presence in Val\'Sharah for hundreds of years. They have never been much more than an occasional nuisance, thus we have tolerated their presence here within these woods.$b$bHowever, something has emboldened them... it feels as though the forest is weakening... they must sense it as well.$b$bThe opportunistic harpies have broken the peace and attacked us in a time of weakness.$b$bHelp us defend Thas\'talah by slaying the invaders.','','','','','E\'lothir, Archdruid of Lore','Return to E\'lothir at Thas\'talah.','21287'),
