('40841','deDE','Val\'sharahs Hilfe','Tötet Raj\'kess und Aufseher Sakar\'thiss an der Bruchküste.','Das Land leidet, $n, und wir spüren seine Qual. Die Druiden von Val\'sharah werden nicht tatenlos zusehen, wie die Heimat unserer Vorfahren von den Naga der Leystacheln zerstört wird.$B$BEs unterliegt unserer Verantwortung, die Natur zu schützen. Diese Naga scheinen sie nur zerstören zu wollen. Wir müssen ihre Anführer niederstrecken und ihre Streitkräfte zurückdrängen.$B$BMit Eurer Hilfe, $n, sind wir vielleicht doch noch in der Lage, dieses Land zu retten.','','','','','','','21737'),
('40841','enUS','The Aid of Val\'sharah','Slay Raj\'kess and Overseer Sakar\'thiss in the Crumbling Coast.','The land is in pain, $n, and we have felt its suffering. The druids of Val\'sharah will not stand idly by and let our ancient home fall to ruin at the hands of the Leyspine naga.$B$BOur charge is to protect nature. These naga seem only to want to destroy it. We must cut down their leaders and drive back their forces.$B$BWith you help, $n, we may still be able to save this land.','','','','','','','21491'),
('40841','esES','La ayuda de Val\'sharah','Mata a Raj\'kess y al sobrestante Sakar\'thiss en la Costa Desmoronada.','La tierra está sufriendo, $n, y hemos sentido su sufrimiento. Los druidas de Val\'sharah no nos quedaremos de brazos cruzados mientras nuestro hogar ancestral sucumbe a manos de los nagas Columnaley.$B$BNuestro cometido es proteger la naturaleza, y parece que esos nagas solo quieren destruirla. Debemos liquidar a sus líderes y hacer retroceder sus fuerzas.$B$BCon tu ayuda, $n, tal vez aún podamos salvar esta tierra.','','','','','','','21737'),
('40841','frFR','Au secours de Val’sharah','Tuez Raj’kess et le Surveillant Sakar’thiss sur la Côte Effritée.','La terre agonise, $n, et nous avons perçu ses souffrances. Les druides de Val’sharah ne resteront pas les bras croisés pendant que les nagas telluréchines ravagent leur sanctuaire ancestral !$B$BNous avons le devoir de protéger la nature. Ces nagas, eux, ne cherchent qu’à la détruire. Il nous faut éliminer leurs chefs et repousser leurs forces.$B$BAvec votre aide, $n, nous avons peut-être encore une chance de sauver ces terres.','','','','','','','21737'),
('40841','ptBR','O Auxílio de Val\'sharah','Mate Raj\'kess e o Feitor Sakar\'thiss na Costa Esfacelada.','A terra agoniza, $n, e nós sentimos seu sofrimento. Os druidas de Val\'sharah não assistirão de braços cruzados à destruição do seu lar ancestral nas mãos das nagas verdespinhas.$B$BAtacaremos para proteger a natureza. Essas nagas parecem que só querem destruí-la. Precisamos derrubar seus líderes e fazer suas forças recuarem.$B$BCom a sua ajuda, $n, talvez ainda possamos salvar esta terra.','','','','','','','21737'),
('40845','deDE','Coastal Healing','Use the Seed Pouch to plant 8 seeds in Sinkholes in the Crumbling Coast.','The earth has suffered wounds at the hands of the Leyspine naga. They have subjugated murlocs to tear up the land and extract its resources for their own devices.$B$B<Lyris hands you a pouch of seeds.>$B$BI have infused these seeds with restorative essences. Place a seed in any scar left by the murlocs and the healing can begin.','','','','','','','21737'),
