('42379','enUS','Growing Power','Use the Ancient Elemental Altar to imbue your artifact, then speak to Advisor Sevel at the Heart of Azeroth.','It appears you & your weapon are both growing in strength. Return to me at the Heart of Azeroth. I have more to show you.','','Return to the Heart of Azeroth when you can, shaman.','Advisor Sevel','','','','21287'),
